    <!-- Official note colors -->
    <!-- We used pastel colors, in HSV space with the following criteria
    All of them have S=65.
    Natural notes have V=85, while sharp notes have V=75
    The hue has been divided between 7 evenly (the natural notes), which is an interval of 51.43
    E is the first one with H=0, F has H=51.43... an so on
    From there, there was also a lot of fine tunning. Final colors in tabbeo_colors_note.xfc in Dropbox-->
